{"TopicId":14069,"ForumId":29,"TopicTitle":"One-part shuttle","CreatedByName":"Vlad. Just Vlad.","CreatedById":12169,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-07-11T15:02:02Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Vlad. Just Vlad.","CreatedById":12169,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-07-11T15:02:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI decided try to make one-part shuttle.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI decided to make It because I don\\\u0027t like a lots of special shuttle-only parts, and I thing it would be great to have one-part shuttle and ships.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAlready done:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E1. Base 3ds max model\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E2. Engine and RCS module\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E3. Toggle code for cargo bay, panels, radiator, etc.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWhat to do:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#008000;\u0022\u003E1. Finish model and textures\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#008000;\u0022\u003E2. Add modules to part.cfg\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#008000;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022text-decoration:line-through;\u0022\u003E3. Finish toggle code\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#FFA500;\u0022\u003E4. Particle effects\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#008000;\u0022\u003EGreen\u003C/span\u003E - I know how to make it\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#FFA500;\u0022\u003EOrange\u003C/span\u003E - I have to figure out how to do it\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EFeatures:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#008000;\u0022\u003EEmergency decouple\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#008000;\u0022\u003ECargo bay\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#008000;\u0022\u003EAirbrake\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#008000;\u0022\u003ESolar panels, radiators.\u003C/span\u003E \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#FFA500;\u0022\u003EMaybe, will functional\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#008000;\u0022\u003EOwn gimbaling axis of each engine.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EDisadvantages of the finished shuttle:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThere won\\\u0027t be smooth animation of models, and rotation of the surfaces. It will toggle\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EShuttle won\\\u0027t have it\\\u0027s own gear\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIn the list of parts will look buggy, in VAB it will look normal\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EDunno, I\\\u0027ll do it at all\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWell, shuttle takes the form:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i41.fastpic.ru/big/2012/0711/e9/89a38c964e0fc7627f634cb7001373e9.jpg\u0022 alt=\u002289a38c964e0fc7627f634cb7001373e9.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"XSP-Xenon Space Programm","CreatedById":8424,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-07-11T19:24:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Ehmmm, I like the idea of this shuttle ;D\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"BlazingAngel665","CreatedById":30182,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-07-11T19:32:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWhat can we do with the cargo bay? will it have radial decouplers for releasing cargo, or the shuttle robotic arm?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vlad. Just Vlad.","CreatedById":12169,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-07-12T10:40:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI know C# very few. There will be only space in cargo bay, decouplers and arms will be istall from other mods and parts.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EShuttle with opened cargo bay and control surfaces in braking mode:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i40.fastpic.ru/big/2012/0712/13/73f2c2d3e4bb2c9af68287b42d5b9d13.jpg\u0022 alt=\u002273f2c2d3e4bb2c9af68287b42d5b9d13.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i40.fastpic.ru/big/2012/0712/91/278af3e7511b6caa1631f8f6550c2a91.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022278af3e7511b6caa1631f8f6550c2a91.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i40.fastpic.ru/big/2012/0712/d1/0374fd5e76e4e6b64b63b00fba1229d1.jpg\u0022 alt=\u00220374fd5e76e4e6b64b63b00fba1229d1.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESolar panels and radiator:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i42.fastpic.ru/big/2012/0712/b3/9634fda3b1c1a869acadb03e2fd9c5b3.jpg\u0022 alt=\u00229634fda3b1c1a869acadb03e2fd9c5b3.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i42.fastpic.ru/big/2012/0712/ce/ce52d0409ea164f90a926f882a6957ce.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022ce52d0409ea164f90a926f882a6957ce.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EBank will change with only upper surfaces. Bottom surface(as you can see, it\\\u0027s one) is needed only for changind pitch and braking.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"BlazingAngel665","CreatedById":30182,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-08-11T03:42:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EImpressive, eagerly awaiting. . .\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}